                          Go Your Own Way!

Now you can take advantage of US Airways GoFares--an affordable way to see your family, visit friends or just go shopping.  GoFares let you travel in many nonstop markets throughout the East and Midwest for as little as $118 roundtrip when you book online at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/gofares.htm by January 24, 2002. So go now and go often. What are you waiting for? 


Fare Details:
-------------
- Tickets must be purchased online no later than Thursday, January 24, 2002
  at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/gofares.htm
- Tickets must be purchased at least 7 days prior to departure
- Travel must be completed by March 19, 2002
- Travel must originate Thursday through Saturday and return Sunday through Tuesday
- Other restrictions apply.  See Sale Fare Requirements below.

This is a sample of the sale fares offered.  For reservations and fares from your city, go to http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/gofares.htm


